members.member:

Selects the specified row range.

The 1-based index of the first row in the range.
/// The 1-based index of the last row in the range.


Scrolls into view.

/// 0-based index
/// The unit type
/// The direction of scrolling
/// The alignment

member.remarks:
Usage example:
var columnToSearch = ColumnToSearch.ByIndex(5);
var columnToSearch = ColumnToSearch.ByHeader("header2", 1);

Usage example:
var textMatch = TextMatch.Match("some text");
var textMatch = TextMatch.Match("some text", 2);

member.summary:
Waits until a response is received from the host and the emulator 
status is set to Ready, or until the timeout is reached, before continuing with the run session.
The default value for milliseconds is 0;
